# Testing

- Functional changes require tests (unit/integration/regression as applicable)
- AI infrastructure tests: Vitest in `.ai/tests/` via `npm run test:ai`
- Bug fixes need a regression test when feasible
- Tests must be deterministic; do not weaken assertions to pass
- Exempt: copy, comments, formatting, docs-only, non-runtime edits
- If coverage is impossible, document technical reason + alternate verification
